snippet.title: F-4C Phantom II / War Thunder 1.91 teaser
snippet.description:
Play for Free Now: https://Warthunder.com/play4free?r=utb_PhantomTheF-4 

Phantom II is a well-known American all-weather supersonic jet interceptor and fighter-bomber. In the upcoming update 1.91 "Night Vision", pilots in War Thunder may look forward to having the chance to sit behind the virtual controls of one of the most recognizable and no less powerful jet aircraft of the 20th century!

🔘 Site: http://warthunder.com/ 
🔘 Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/warthunder
🔘 Twitter: http://twitter.com/warthunder
🔘 Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/WarThunder
🔘 Forum: http://forum.warthunder.com/

#WarThunder #Phantom
